  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the possible harvest of a tensor fasciae latae flap
      based on septocutaneous perforators.This study should further confirm our data from an
      anatomical study concerning location, distribution, diameter and differentiation of the
      perforators.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
